	* xdisp.c (remember_mouse_glyph): Handle ON_RIGHT_DIVIDER and
	ON_BOTTOM_DIVIDER cases.
	* window.c (coordinates_in_window): Return ON_VERTICAL_BORDER
	only if the window has no right divider.
