	* Makefile.in (NOTIFY_OBJ): New variable.
	(base_obj): Replace inotify.o by $(NOTIFY_OBJ).

	* emacs.c (main): Use HAVE_W32NOTIFY to wrap respective code.
	Call syms_of_gfilenotify.

