	* nsfns.m (ns_tooltip): Initialize.

2013-04-28  Eli Zaretskii  <eliz@gnu.org>

	* coding.c (decode_coding_gap): Don't remove the character before
	a newline unless it's a CR character.  (Bug#14287)

