2013-03-28  Stefan Monnier  <monnier@iro.umontreal.ca>

	* lisp.h (save_type, XSAVE_POINTER, set_save_pointer, XSAVE_INTEGER)
	(set_save_integer, XSAVE_OBJECT, XSAVE_VALUE): Move to avoid
